OL,6,FCriminals are using AI to clone
OL,7,Fpeople's voices and set up
OL,8,Funauthorised direct debits over the
OL,9,Fphone, National Trading Standards
OL,10,F(NTS) has warned.
OL,12,FNTS said "advanced" voice cloning was
OL,13,Fpart of an organised criminal
OL,14,Foperation that appeared to be
OL,15,Ftargeting older people.
OL,17,FFraudsters began the process by asking
OL,18,Fvictims to participate in a so-called
OL,19,F"lifestyle survey" phone call, which
OL,20,Fwas actually designed to gather
OL,21,Fpersonal, health and financial details.
