OL,3,CCriminals using AI to clone voices and
OL,4,Cset up direct debits
OL,6,FThe criminals then used this
OL,7,Finformation to create AI-generated
OL,8,Fvoice clones to simulate consent for
OL,9,Fdirect debits.
OL,11,FThe voice clones could then be used to
OL,12,Fset up payments with banks and other
OL,13,Flegitimate businesses and financial
OL,14,Fproviders without the victim's
OL,15,Fknowledge, NTS said.
OL,17,FVictims often did not realise payments
OL,18,Fwere being taken, it warned.
