OL,6,FLatest figures from NTS suggests that
OL,7,FUK adults now receive an average of
OL,8,Fseven scam calls or texts per month,
OL,9,Fwith about one in five (21%) receiving
OL,10,Fthem most days and 9% receiving them
OL,11,Fevery day.
OL,13,FNTS said it blocked almost 21 million
OL,14,Fscam phone calls and shut down 2,000
OL,15,Fnumbers in a six-month period.
OL,17,FLouise Baxter, head of the NTS scams
OL,18,Fteam, said: "What we're seeing is a
OL,19,Fdeeply disturbing combination of old
OL,20,Fand new: traditional phone scams
OL,21,Fsupported by disturbing new techniques.
