OL,6,F"Criminals are using AI not just to
OL,7,Fdeceive victims, but to trick
OL,8,Flegitimate systems into processing
OL,9,Ffraudulent payments.
OL,11,F"This is no longer just a nuisance `
OL,12,Fit's a co-ordinated, sophisticated
OL,13,Foperation targeting some of the most
OL,14,Fsituationally vulnerable consumers in
OL,15,Fsociety.
OL,17,F"We urge everyone to speak to friends
OL,18,Fand relatives about scam calls, check
OL,19,Fbank statements regularly and report
OL,20,Fanything suspicious."
