OL,6,FJohn Herriman, chief executive at the
OL,7,FChartered Trading Standards Institute
OL,8,F(CTSI), said: "This alarming new twist
OL,9,Fin phone-based fraud shows just how
OL,10,Fquickly criminals are exploiting
OL,11,Femerging technologies to prey on the
OL,12,Fpublic.
OL,14,F"Voice cloning takes scam calls to a
OL,15,Fsinister new level, making it even
OL,16,Fharder for legitimate businesses and
OL,17,Fconsumers to distinguish real
OL,18,Finteractions from fraudulent ones.
