OL,6,F"If you see any direct debits or
OL,7,Ftransactions on your bank account that
OL,8,Fyou don't recognise, contact your bank
OL,9,Fimmediately using the number on the
OL,10,Fback of your card. You should also
OL,11,Freport any scams to Police Scotland or
OL,12,FReport Fraud to investigate.
OL,14,F"It's also worth making sure you're
OL,15,Fregistered with the telephone
OL,16,Fpreference service to opt out of
OL,17,Funsolicited marketing calls, that way
OL,18,Fyou'll know that any unexpected
OL,19,Fmarketing or sales calls are either a
OL,20,Frogue company or a scammer."
